  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK278">
<l>maṉattatu mācāka māṇṭārnī rāṭi</l>
<l>maṟaintoḻuku māntar palar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are many men of masked conduct, who perform their ablutions, and (make a show) of greatness, while their mind is defiled (with guilt).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
